STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Basilis S. STEPHANATOS, Defendant-Movant. M-135/136/137 September Term 2018
081583 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 23, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file an over length brief (M-135) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motions for leave to appeal (M-136) and for stay (M-137) are denied; and it is further

ORDERED that the January 22, 2019 trial date is a peremptory date.
